<h3>Email is the official means of communication to students and employees. You are responsible to check it frequently.</h3>
<p> </p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;">Use the following steps to access your BYU-Idaho Email</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;">1. Go to <a href="http://my.byui.edu">my.byu.edu</a></p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;">2. Log-in with your BYU-Idaho user-name and password</p>
<p style="padding-left: 60px;">3. Click on the email tab</p>
<p> </p>
